SUMMARY:Charter Review Commission Meeting
LOCATION:Tampa Old City Hall - Sister Cities Room 315 East Kennedy Bouleva
 rd Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:CHARTER REVIEW ADVISORY COMMISSION MEETING Date: Tuesday\, Jun
 e 9\, 2026 Time: 6:00pm to 9:00pm Location: Old City Hall  Sister Cities R
 oom 315 East Kennedy Boulevard Tampa\, Florida 33602 Facilitator Robert He
 ndrickson will facilitate meetings of the 2025 Charter Review Advisory Com
 mission. The commissions purpose is to review the Tampa Home Rule Charter 
 of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by majority
  vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendations 
 to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be placed o
 n the ballot for a vote on March 2\, 2027. Meetings are scheduled monthly 
 for the 2 nd and 4 th Tuesday. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/1
 80071
