SUMMARY:Expressive Poetry
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Since ancient times\, humans have created meaning of our world
  and the afterlife through the art of poetic expression. This River of My 
 Life: A Poetic Expression Workshop will engage students in communicating w
 ith ancient artworks through poetic writing\, inspired by the Mysteries of
  the Nile: Ancient Egypt exhibition. Through the use of stream of consciou
 sness and ekphrastic poetry activities\, students will be able to express 
